.SH TROUBLESHOOTING
.TP
.B "No windows found"
Ensure you have visible, non-minimized windows open. The tool only processes windows that are currently viewable.

.TP
.B "Permission errors"
Make sure you're running in an X11 session with proper display access. Check that DISPLAY environment variable is set correctly.

.TP
.B "Import errors"
Install required dependencies:
.B pip install python-xlib psutil

.TP
.B "Windows not tiling correctly"
Check that windows are not maximized or in fullscreen mode, as these states may interfere with tiling operations.

